#: ../../user/running.rst:3
msgid "Running Experiments"
msgstr "執行實驗"

#: ../../user/running.rst:6
msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "目錄"

#: ../../user/running.rst:8
msgid ""
"One of the best ways to get a feel for deep RL is to run the algorithms "
"and see how they perform on different tasks. The Spinning Up code library"
" makes small-scale (local) experiments easy to do, and in this section, "
"we'll discuss two ways to run them: either from the command line, or "
"through function calls in scripts."
msgstr ""
"要深入了解深度強化學習 (deep RL)，最好的方式之一就是執行演算法並觀察它們在不同任務上的表現。"
"Spinning Up 程式庫讓小規模（本地）實驗變得容易進行，"
"在本節中，我們將討論兩種執行方式：從命令列執行，或透過腳本中的函式呼叫執行。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:12
msgid "Launching from the Command Line"
msgstr "從命令列啟動"

#: ../../user/running.rst:15
msgid ""
"Spinning Up ships with ``spinup/run.py``, a convenient tool that lets you"
" easily launch any algorithm (with any choices of hyperparameters) from "
"the command line. It also serves as a thin wrapper over the utilities for"
" watching trained policies and plotting, although we will not discuss "
"that functionality on this page (for those details, see the pages on "
"`experiment outputs`_ and `plotting`_)."
msgstr ""
"Spinning Up 附帶了 ``spinup/run.py``，這是一個方便的工具，"
"讓你可以從命令列輕鬆啟動任何演算法（使用任意超參數 (hyperparameter) 選擇）。"
"它也是觀察已訓練策略和繪圖工具的輕量封裝，"
"不過我們不會在本頁討論該功能（詳情請參閱 `experiment outputs`_ 和 `plotting`_ 頁面）。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:17
msgid "The standard way to run a Spinning Up algorithm from the command line is"
msgstr "從命令列執行 Spinning Up 演算法的標準方式是"

#: ../../user/running.rst:23
msgid "eg:"
msgstr "例如："

#: ../../user/running.rst:32 ../../user/running.rst:96
#: ../../user/running.rst:106
msgid "You Should Know"
msgstr "你應該知道"

#: ../../user/running.rst:34
msgid ""
"If you are using ZShell: ZShell interprets square brackets as special "
"characters. Spinning Up uses square brackets in a few ways for command "
"line arguments; make sure to escape them, or try the solution recommended"
" `here <http://kinopyo.com/en/blog/escape-square-bracket-by-default-in-"
"zsh>`_ if you want to escape them by default."
msgstr ""
"如果你使用 ZShell：ZShell 會將方括號視為特殊字元。"
"Spinning Up 在命令列引數中以幾種方式使用方括號；請確保對它們進行跳脫，"
"或者如果你想預設跳脫方括號，可以嘗試 `這裡 <http://kinopyo.com/en/blog/escape-square-bracket-by-default-in-"
"zsh>`_ 推薦的解決方案。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:36
msgid "Detailed Quickstart Guide"
msgstr "詳細快速入門指南"

#: ../../user/running.rst:44
msgid ""
"runs PPO in the ``Ant-v2`` Gym environment, with various settings "
"controlled by the flags."
msgstr ""
"在 ``Ant-v2`` Gym 環境中執行 PPO，各種設定由旗標控制。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:46
msgid ""
"By default, the PyTorch version will run (except for with TRPO, since "
"Spinning Up doesn't have a PyTorch TRPO yet). Substitute ``ppo`` with "
"``ppo_tf1`` for the Tensorflow version."
msgstr ""
"預設情況下會執行 PyTorch 版本（TRPO 除外，因為 Spinning Up 尚未提供 PyTorch 版的 TRPO）。"
"若要使用 Tensorflow 版本，請將 ``ppo`` 替換為 ``ppo_tf1``。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:48
msgid ""
"``clip_ratio``, ``hid``, and ``act`` are flags to set some algorithm "
"hyperparameters. You can provide multiple values for hyperparameters to "
"run multiple experiments. Check the docs to see what hyperparameters you "
"can set (click here for the `PPO documentation`_)."
msgstr ""
"``clip_ratio``、``hid`` 和 ``act`` 是用於設定部分演算法超參數的旗標。"
"你可以為超參數提供多個值以執行多個實驗。"
"請查閱文件以了解可設定的超參數（點此查看 `PPO documentation`_）。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:50
msgid ""
"``hid`` and ``act`` are `special shortcut flags`_ for setting the hidden "
"sizes and activation function for the neural networks trained by the "
"algorithm."
msgstr ""
"``hid`` 和 ``act`` 是 `special shortcut flags`_，"
"用於設定演算法所訓練的神經網路的隱藏層大小和激活函數。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:52
msgid ""
"The ``seed`` flag sets the seed for the random number generator. RL "
"algorithms have high variance, so try multiple seeds to get a feel for "
"how performance varies."
msgstr ""
"``seed`` 旗標設定隨機數產生器的種子。"
"RL 演算法具有很高的變異性，因此可以嘗試多個種子來了解效能的變化情況。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:54
msgid ""
"The ``dt`` flag ensures that the save directory names will have "
"timestamps in them (otherwise they don't, unless you set "
"``FORCE_DATESTAMP=True`` in ``spinup/user_config.py``)."
msgstr ""
"``dt`` 旗標確保儲存目錄名稱中包含時間戳記"
"（否則不會包含，除非你在 ``spinup/user_config.py`` 中設定 ``FORCE_DATESTAMP=True``）。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:56
msgid ""
"The ``data_dir`` flag allows you to set the save folder for results. The "
"default value is set by ``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR`` in "
"``spinup/user_config.py``, which will be a subfolder ``data`` in the "
"``spinningup`` folder (unless you change it)."
msgstr ""
"``data_dir`` 旗標允許你設定結果的儲存資料夾。"
"預設值由 ``spinup/user_config.py`` 中的 ``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR`` 設定，"
"預設為 ``spinningup`` 資料夾下的 ``data`` 子資料夾（除非你修改它）。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:58
msgid ""
"`Save directory names`_ are based on ``exp_name`` and any flags which "
"have multiple values. Instead of the full flag, a shorthand will appear "
"in the directory name. Shorthands can be provided by the user in square "
"brackets after the flag, like ``--hid[h]``; otherwise, shorthands are "
"substrings of the flag (``clip_ratio`` becomes ``cli``). To illustrate, "
"the save directory for the run with ``clip_ratio=0.1``, ``hid=[32,32]``, "
"and ``seed=10`` will be:"
msgstr ""
"`Save directory names`_ 基於 ``exp_name`` 以及具有多個值的旗標。"
"目錄名稱中會使用簡寫而非完整的旗標名稱。"
"使用者可以在旗標後的方括號中提供簡寫，如 ``--hid[h]``；"
"否則，簡寫會是旗標的子字串（``clip_ratio`` 會變成 ``cli``）。"
"舉例來說，``clip_ratio=0.1``、``hid=[32,32]`` 和 ``seed=10`` 的執行，"
"其儲存目錄會是："

