msgid ""
"If you run ``python -m spinup.run [algo]`` without ``_pytorch`` or "
"``_tf1``, the runner will look in ``spinup/user_config.py`` for which "
"version it should default to for that algorithm."
msgstr ""
"如果執行 ``python -m spinup.run [algo]`` 時未加上 ``_pytorch`` 或 ``_tf1``，"
"執行器會在 ``spinup/user_config.py`` 中查找該演算法應預設使用的版本。"

