#: ../../user/running.rst:133
msgid ""
"Experiments don't launch in parallel because they soak up enough "
"resources that executing several at the same time wouldn't get a speedup."
msgstr ""
"實驗不會平行啟動，因為它們會消耗大量資源，同時執行多個實驗不會帶來加速效果。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:138
msgid "Special Flags"
msgstr "特殊旗標"

#: ../../user/running.rst:140
msgid "A few flags receive special treatment."
msgstr "有幾個旗標會受到特殊處理。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:144
msgid "Environment Flag"
msgstr "環境旗標"

#: ../../user/running.rst:148
msgid ""
"*string*. The name of an environment in the OpenAI Gym. All Spinning Up "
"algorithms are implemented as functions that accept ``env_fn`` as an "
"argument, where ``env_fn`` must be a callable function that builds a copy"
" of the RL environment. Since the most common use case is Gym "
"environments, though, all of which are built through "
"``gym.make(env_name)``, we allow you to just specify ``env_name`` (or "
"``env`` for short) at the command line, which gets converted to a lambda-"
"function that builds the correct gym environment."
msgstr ""
"*string*。OpenAI Gym 中的環境名稱。所有 Spinning Up 演算法都實作為接受 ``env_fn`` "
"引數的函式，其中 ``env_fn`` 必須是一個可呼叫函式，用於建構 RL 環境的副本。"
"不過，由於最常見的使用情境是 Gym 環境，而這些環境都是透過 ``gym.make(env_name)`` "
"建構的，因此我們允許你在命令列中僅指定 ``env_name``（或簡寫為 ``env``），"
"它會被轉換為一個建構正確 Gym 環境的 lambda 函式。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:152
msgid "Shortcut Flags"
msgstr "捷徑旗標"

#: ../../user/running.rst:154
msgid ""
"Some algorithm arguments are relatively long, and we enabled shortcuts "
"for them:"
msgstr "部分演算法引數名稱較長，我們為它們提供了捷徑："

#: ../../user/running.rst:158
msgid ""
"*list of ints*. Sets the sizes of the hidden layers in the neural "
"networks (policies and value functions)."
msgstr ""
"*list of ints*。設定神經網路（策略和價值函數）中隱藏層的大小。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:162
msgid ""
"*tf op*. The activation function for the neural networks in the actor and"
" critic."
msgstr "*tf op*。演員 (actor) 和評論家 (critic) 神經網路的激活函數。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:164
msgid "These flags are valid for all current Spinning Up algorithms."
msgstr "這些旗標適用於所有目前的 Spinning Up 演算法。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:167
msgid "Config Flags"
msgstr "設定旗標"

#: ../../user/running.rst:169
msgid ""
"These flags are not hyperparameters of any algorithm, but change the "
"experimental configuration in some way."
msgstr "這些旗標不是任何演算法的超參數，而是以某種方式更改實驗配置。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:173
msgid ""
"*int*. If this flag is set, the experiment is launched with this many "
"processes, one per cpu, connected by MPI. Some algorithms are amenable to"
" this sort of parallelization but not all. An error will be raised if you"
" try setting ``num_cpu`` > 1 for an incompatible algorithm. You can also "
"set ``--num_cpu auto``, which will automatically use as many CPUs as are "
"available on the machine."
msgstr ""
"*int*。如果設定此旗標，實驗會以指定數量的處理程序啟動，每個 CPU 一個，透過 MPI 連接。"
"部分演算法適合這種平行化方式，但並非全部。"
"如果你嘗試對不相容的演算法設定 ``num_cpu`` > 1，會引發錯誤。"
"你也可以設定 ``--num_cpu auto``，這會自動使用機器上可用的所有 CPU。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:177
msgid ""
"*string*. The experiment name. This is used in naming the save directory "
"for each experiment. The default is \"cmd\" + [algo name]."
msgstr ""
"*string*。實驗名稱。用於命名每個實驗的儲存目錄。預設值為 \"cmd\" + [演算法名稱]。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:181
msgid ""
"*path*. Set the base save directory for this experiment or set of "
"experiments. If none is given, the ``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR`` in "
"``spinup/user_config.py`` will be used."
msgstr ""
"*path*。設定此實驗或實驗組的基底儲存目錄。"
"如果未指定，將使用 ``spinup/user_config.py`` 中的 ``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR``。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:185
msgid ""
"*bool*. Include date and time in the name for the save directory of the "
"experiment."
msgstr "*bool*。在實驗的儲存目錄名稱中包含日期和時間。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:189
msgid "Where Results are Saved"
msgstr "結果儲存位置"

#: ../../user/running.rst:191
msgid ""
"Results for a particular experiment (a single run of a configuration of "
"hyperparameters) are stored in"
msgstr "特定實驗（一組超參數配置的單次執行）的結果儲存在"

