"``data_dir`` is the value of the ``--data_dir`` flag (defaults to "
"``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR`` from ``spinup/user_config.py`` if ``--data_dir`` is "
"not given),"
msgstr ""
"``data_dir`` 是 ``--data_dir`` 旗標的值"
"（如果未指定 ``--data_dir``，則預設為 ``spinup/user_config.py`` 中的 ``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR``），"

#: ../../user/running.rst:200
msgid ""
"the ``outer_prefix`` is a ``YY-MM-DD_`` timestamp if the ``--datestamp`` "
"flag is raised, otherwise nothing,"
msgstr ""
"``outer_prefix`` 在啟用 ``--datestamp`` 旗標時為 ``YY-MM-DD_`` 時間戳記，否則為空，"

#: ../../user/running.rst:201
msgid ""
"the ``inner_prefix`` is a ``YY-MM-DD_HH-MM-SS-`` timestamp if the "
"``--datestamp`` flag is raised, otherwise nothing,"
msgstr ""
"``inner_prefix`` 在啟用 ``--datestamp`` 旗標時為 ``YY-MM-DD_HH-MM-SS-`` 時間戳記，否則為空，"

#: ../../user/running.rst:202
msgid ""
"and ``suffix`` is a special string based on the experiment "
"hyperparameters."
msgstr "``suffix`` 是根據實驗超參數產生的特殊字串。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:205
msgid "How is Suffix Determined?"
msgstr "後綴是如何決定的？"

#: ../../user/running.rst:207
msgid ""
"Suffixes are only included if you run multiple experiments at once, and "
"they only include references to hyperparameters that differ across "
"experiments, except for random seed. The goal is to make sure that "
"results for similar experiments (ones which share all params except seed)"
" are grouped in the same folder."
msgstr ""
"後綴僅在你同時執行多個實驗時才會包含，而且只包含各實驗間不同的超參數"
"（隨機種子除外）的引用。目的是確保相似的實驗"
"（除種子外所有參數都相同的實驗）的結果被歸類在同一個資料夾中。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:209
msgid ""
"Suffixes are constructed by combining *shorthands* for hyperparameters "
"with their values, where a shorthand is either 1) constructed "
"automatically from the hyperparameter name or 2) supplied by the user. "
"The user can supply a shorthand by writing in square brackets after the "
"kwarg flag."
msgstr ""
"後綴由超參數的*簡寫*與其值組合而成，簡寫可以是 1) 從超參數名稱自動產生，"
"或 2) 由使用者提供。使用者可以在關鍵字引數旗標後的方括號中提供簡寫。"

