#: ../../user/running.rst:231
msgid "Extra"
msgstr "補充"

#: ../../user/running.rst:233
msgid "You Don't Actually Need to Know This One"
msgstr "這個你其實不需要知道"

#: ../../user/running.rst:235
msgid ""
"Each individual algorithm is located in a file "
"``spinup/algos/BACKEND/ALGO_NAME/ALGO_NAME.py``, and these files can be "
"run directly from the command line with a limited set of arguments (some "
"of which differ from what's available to ``spinup/run.py``). The command "
"line support in the individual algorithm files is essentially vestigial, "
"however, and this is **not** a recommended way to perform experiments."
msgstr ""
"每個演算法位於 ``spinup/algos/BACKEND/ALGO_NAME/ALGO_NAME.py`` 檔案中，"
"這些檔案可以從命令列直接執行，但支援的引數有限"
"（部分引數與 ``spinup/run.py`` 提供的不同）。"
"然而，個別演算法檔案中的命令列支援基本上是遺留功能，"
"**不**建議以此方式進行實驗。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:237
msgid ""
"This documentation page will not describe those command line calls, and "
"will *only* describe calls through ``spinup/run.py``."
msgstr ""
"本文件頁面不會描述那些命令列呼叫方式，*僅*描述透過 ``spinup/run.py`` 的呼叫。"

