#: ../../user/running.rst:264
msgid "Using ExperimentGrid"
msgstr "使用 ExperimentGrid"

#: ../../user/running.rst:266
msgid ""
"It's often useful in machine learning research to run the same algorithm "
"with many possible hyperparameters. Spinning Up ships with a simple tool "
"for facilitating this, called `ExperimentGrid`_."
msgstr ""
"在機器學習研究中，使用多種超參數組合執行相同演算法通常很有用。"
"Spinning Up 附帶了一個簡單的工具來協助此功能，名為 `ExperimentGrid`_。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:269
msgid "Consider the example in ``spinup/examples/pytorch/bench_ppo_cartpole.py``:"
msgstr "以 ``spinup/examples/pytorch/bench_ppo_cartpole.py`` 中的範例為例："

#: ../../user/running.rst:294
msgid ""
"(An equivalent Tensorflow example is available in "
"``spinup/examples/tf1/bench_ppo_cartpole.py``.)"
msgstr ""
"（等效的 Tensorflow 範例可在 ``spinup/examples/tf1/bench_ppo_cartpole.py`` 中找到。）"

#: ../../user/running.rst:296
msgid "After making the ExperimentGrid object, parameters are added to it with"
msgstr "建立 ExperimentGrid 物件後，透過以下方式新增參數"

#: ../../user/running.rst:302
msgid ""
"where ``in_name`` forces a parameter to appear in the experiment name, "
"even if it has the same value across all experiments."
msgstr ""
"其中 ``in_name`` 強制將參數顯示在實驗名稱中，即使該參數在所有實驗中的值都相同。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:304
msgid "After all parameters have been added,"
msgstr "在所有參數都新增完畢後，"

#: ../../user/running.rst:310
msgid ""
"runs all experiments in the grid (one experiment per valid "
"configuration), by providing the configurations as kwargs to the function"
" ``thunk``. ``ExperimentGrid.run`` uses a function named "
"`call_experiment`_ to launch ``thunk``, and ``**run_kwargs`` specify "
"behaviors for ``call_experiment``. See `the documentation page`_ for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"透過將配置作為關鍵字引數傳遞給函式 ``thunk``，"
"執行網格中的所有實驗（每個有效配置一個實驗）。"
"``ExperimentGrid.run`` 使用名為 `call_experiment`_ 的函式來啟動 ``thunk``，"
"``**run_kwargs`` 指定 ``call_experiment`` 的行為。詳情請參閱 `the documentation page`_。"

#: ../../user/running.rst:312
msgid ""
"Except for the absence of shortcut kwargs (you can't use ``hid`` for "
"``ac_kwargs:hidden_sizes`` in ``ExperimentGrid``), the basic behavior of "
"``ExperimentGrid`` is the same as running things from the command line. "
"(In fact, ``spinup.run`` uses an ``ExperimentGrid`` under the hood.)"
msgstr ""
"除了沒有捷徑關鍵字引數（在 ``ExperimentGrid`` 中不能用 ``hid`` 代替 "
"``ac_kwargs:hidden_sizes``）之外，``ExperimentGrid`` 的基本行為與從命令列執行相同。"
"（事實上，``spinup.run`` 底層就是使用 ``ExperimentGrid``。）"
